              '\n'
              '   Me: Haha, yes, I know that much.\n'
              '\n'
              '   Her: O, well that explains it. We are in NEW ZEALAND.\n'
              '\n'
              '   Me: Wait. what.\n'
              '\n'
              '   Me: Wait. WHAT.\n'
              '\n'
