              '   just yet.  So--Ill just tell you what Ive been up to.\n'
              '\n'
              '   I woke up in Nairobi at around 11:00am on Thursday, January '
              '5^th.  I\n'
              '   really hadnt slept much in the previous, say, 3 weeks, out of '
