              '   Limbless Beggars, and Volcanoes - Part 1 February 9, 2012\n'
              '\n'
              '   Good evening all.  Im at the same cafe in Kabale, Uganda, and '
              'I feel\n'
              '   like blogging a bit more.  The owners of this cafe are '
