              '   probably our best so far.\n'
              '\n'
              '   After 200km, we arrived in Bahia Blanca.  Leo dropped us off '
              'near a\n'
              '   hostel, which came recommended by a French couple that Pete '
              'had met.\n'
              '   The hostel was full, but they had room for our tents.  We '
