              '   America.\n'
              '\n'
              '   The train was supposed to take 14 hours, and was built in '
              '1965.  We\n'
              '   boarded around 7:40PM.  Most of the windows were cracked, and '
              'the thing\n'
              '   was in desperate need of a wash.  They had a dining car '
