              '\n'
              '\n'
              '   Backpacking.  What its all about.  El Chaltn, Argentina.\n'
              '\n'
              '   More dulce de leche ice cream.  Argentina, of course.\n'
              '\n'
              '   I dont imagine the overt enthusiasm pumping this post was the '
