              '   fee, that very morning.\n'
              '\n'
              '   To this, I innocently yet correctly respond that the '
              'managerial issue\n'
              '   has nothing to do with race, but rather, passport: if I had '
              'a\n'
              '   Senegalese passport, it would be hard for me to go to the USA '
